Description copied from class: DataMappingProvider
Gather the mappings. The method returns the mapping type, determining whether the mappings are added to the database "as is" or whether they are materialized (=applied) to the underlying database. In case no mapping type is returned, DEFAULT_MAPPING_TYPE is used.
